reviews.review_text: As a man who just turned 40 and has never been to a gym in his life, doing three personal trainer sessions really helped me get started and gave me the confidence to go to the gym regularly. My trainer Dylan Hunt was absolutely fantastic and always checks in on me when he sees me at the gym. This is a really busy gym but they make sure you feel a part of the community and everyone is super helpful. Big shout out to Dylan though, he made everything super easy to understand and gave me a great work out plan. I love catching up with him when I see him
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Alan, We are so happy to see your feedback and glad that you enjoy your personal training sessions with Dylan! It is never too late to start weight training and taking care of your health :) This is what we take pride of as a trainer is to help our clients to achieve their fitness goals. Again, thank you for your positive comments. Enjoy your workout! Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: Jogpaul is an exceptional personal trainer! His dedication and expertise transformed my fitness journey, helping me reach goals I never thought possible. The results speak volumes, and I couldnt be happier with my progress. Highly recommended for anyone seeking a motivating and knowledgeable fitness partner!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Thezyth, Thank you for your positive feedback. We are extremely happy that you are seeing results with our personal trainer Jogpaul. Our personal trainer do provide a great training program with nutrition supports to help our clients to achieve their fitness goals! Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: Newcomer to the gym, delighted with the facilities! Great experience with PT Alex S who ran through a personal trainer session with me. Showed a great mix of technical knowledge, enthusiasm, and support that made it so enjoyable! Really happy with things
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Michael, Thank you for your review! We love hearing from our members, especially newcomers when we are able to make a positive change in your fitness experience! I know Alex S works super hard to help our members and clients to achieve your fitness goals, so Ill be sure to pass off your positive feedback to him and the team. Thanks again, Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: Jogpaul is the best personal trainer out there! If you re looking to get a personal trainer, highly recommend asking for him. My goal was to put on more muscle and we did exactly that. All of our sessions were fun and challenging at the same time. Definitely made me look forward to our sessions. I would recommend him to my friends and family.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Simran, This review made our day! Its always great to hear how our personal trainer can help our members to accomplish their fitness goals! I know Jogpaul really makes a difference with his clients and provides quality service. Thank you for your support and review. Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: I recommend this gym - Ive been taking PT with Jogpaul for a couple of months and have only praise to share! Hes a genuine guy that wont beat around the bush - his straightforward demeanor and approach to training makes working out with him effective. Its refreshing to see a PT with real passion behind his work and it absolutely shows in what he puts on the table and the energy he brings to sessions
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Ryan, Thank you for your review and we are glad that you enjoy your training sessions with Jogpaul! Passion is one of our core values in Fitness World! We do take pride of that and help our clients to success! Thanks again for your review, Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: Went to the gym here, not very confident in myself for exercises and would be worried about not doing them right! Met a personal trainer there by the name of PT Alex, the experience and quality of not only his communication and understanding but showing me all the exercises was the best iv ever seen! He trained me that day to help me get a better understanding of all the workouts best for me and exactly what I should be doing! I am 100% going back and getting sessions with him and I couldn t recommend him highly enough! An absolutely gent of a lad with massive knowledge of the exercises and helping you understand your goals! Would definitely recommend anyone that wants the better themselves (regardless of confidence) ask for Alex! 10/10
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Alan, This review made our day! Alex is definitely one of our great trainers that make a difference in our clients fitness goals! His clients has been seeing results since working with him. And we are glad that we are being part of your fitness journey. Have a great day, and thanks for the review! Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: I just worked out here for the first time and it was a great experience. The girl at the front desk (I believe her name is Sahar) was amazing and gave me a great tour of the gym. This place is pretty huge and it has more than enough equipment to accommodate for everyone. They even have massage machines and a womens only section. Check it out! I ll definitely be back next week to sign up for a membership :)
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Matt, Thank you for your review. We are glad that you had such a great experience on your first visit. Besides our large variety of equipment, we do have recovery tools such as hydro massage and normatic leg compression that helps a lot with muscle recovery. We are more than happy to assist you with your membership sign-up. You can call us or send me an email at GMKitsilano@fitnessworld.ca for membership sign-up appointment :) General Manager Eve

reviews.review_text: All the staff here are great and I have been especially impressed by Hazel who is so welcoming every day and creates such a comfortable, friendly environment as soon as you walk through the door! She has such a positive attitude!!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Rebecca, Thank you for your great review! We are glad that hear our front desk staff Hazel make such a positive influence to you. Our staffs take pride of helping our members. Welcome to our club any day and time! Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: Dylan is an incredible trainer.  He really pays attention to your goals and creates workouts specifically designed to meet those goals.  He is a pleasure to work with. I would definitely  recommend him as a personal trainer!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Susan, Thank you for your recommendation and review. We are very happy to hear that you had great personal training sessions with our trainer Dylan. We take pride of helping members to achieve their fitness goals! It is our pleasure to be part of your fitness journey! Have a great day, Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: I highly recommend Jogpaul as a personal trainer. His expertise in fitness is unmatched. Hes incredibly easy to work with, always adapting to my needs and goals. Jogpauls unwavering support and positive attitude have been instrumental in my fitness journey. I couldnt have asked for a better trainer.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Vikk, Thank you for your positive feedback with our personal trainer Jogpaul. He puts his heart to his client and makes sure he helps his clients to achieve their fitness goals! Again, thank you for your 5 star reviews with our personal training service! Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: I got Jogpaul as my personal trainer and hes exceptional! He gives the best advice ive ever received for fitness and still maintains a good relationship with his clients outside of the workout. His motivating energy left me with results past me would be proud of alongside Jogpaul himself. If you get the chance to choose your PT, I couldnt recommend anyone else more.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Shei, Thank you for your review and we are glad that you enjoyed the personal training sessions with Jogpaul. We appreciate the kind words! This totally made our day when we heard about our personal training clients are satisfied and get to their fitness goals! Have a great day, and thanks for the review again! Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: Dylan is an absolute joy to have as a PT . He s professional, patient, knowledgeable and will make the whole experience for you so much fun . He also pushes you to work hard and will ensure sure that you reach your goals. I owe every inch of success to him , 100% recommend
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Hannah, Thank you for your review! This is wonderful to hear that our trainer Dylan has helped you to achieve your fitness goals! We always love to make clients workout plan fun and professional! Enjoy your workout and thanks for your recommendation. Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: I had an amazing experience with my PT Jogpaul D! Jogpaul is super knowledgeable, motivating, and really pushed me to reach my fitness goals. He personalized my workouts and provided valuable guidance throughout my fitness journey. I highly recommend him to anyone looking for a dedicated and supportive trainer!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Baljyot, Thank you for your amazing review! We really appreciate your kind words. Jogpaul is one of our best trainers to train with! Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: I ve been training with Jogpaul for almost 2 months now and I can t say enough about how helpful he has been to me. He s helped me find the right balance with work, social and gym life. He s pushed me to understand failure and I ve seen unreal results in such a short space of time. I m excited for what s next and couldn t recommend him enough for anybody considering personal training.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Ryan, Thank you for review. This review made our day! Its always great to see our personal training client get their results and see the difference in progress! We are excited to see your next step of your fitness journey and Jogpaul will help you along the way! Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: Delighted to have Chloe as my PT for the past couple of months - her professionalism along with mountains of expertise on nutrition, goal setting, targeted training methods to even out imbalances and her clarity in explaining proper form/technique has been refreshing. I would highly recommend her to anyone looking for a tailored plan, no matter what your level is! What truly sets Chloe apart is her ability to motivate and inspire. She genuinely cares about her clients goals and aspirations and goes above and beyond to keep me motivated. Her positive attitude, energy, and unwavering support has created an environment where I feel encouraged to push myself even after a long day of work.

Awesome gym for the monthly fee. The PT I ve done with Adam for the past 6 months has really boosted my confidence using the broad range of equipment available (and gyms in general) and given me a lot of new routines I wouldn t have put together on my own and also helped nutrition advice that wraps around my busy schedule to help me with my goals. Highly recommended!

I cant say enough good things about Jogpaul! He is hands down the best personal trainer in the industry. Thanks to his expertise and dedication, Ive not only achieved my fitness goals but also become stronger than I ever thought possible. Jogpauls personalized training programs are second to none. His encouragement and support every step of the way have been instrumental in my fitness journey. Whether youre a beginner or a seasoned fitness enthusiast, Jogpaul tailors his workouts to suit your needs and abilities. I wholeheartedly recommend Jogpaul to everyone looking to improve their fitness and overall well-being. You wont find a more dedicated and knowledgeable trainer than Jogpaul. Thank you, for helping me reach new heights in my fitness journey. You truly are the best!
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Varun, It is very nice of your words and review! Helping our personal training client with our training program and nutrition coaching is something that we take pride in, so to hear that its working for you with Jogpaul! Thanks again for your review! Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: My experience with Fitness World Kitsilano has been and continues to be perfect. From the work outs, to the amazing trainers! A special shout out to one of the trainers Chloe. She is extremely professional, motivating, knowledgeable and encouraging. She knows how to push you to the limit in the best way possible with your workouts. Chloe really care and go above and beyond to help you achieve your goals.  Highly recommended! Thank you!

I took some personal training sessions with Ashley here after the recommendation of a friend and, without any exaggeration, she has changed my life for the better and helped set me on my own path to a healthier life. I really connect with Ashleys approach and vibe, as I find most trainers a little too rah-rah and come across a bit fake, so Ashleys kindness, transparency, and easy-going personality are strong motivators to keep it up. And on top of physical results, Im seeing strong mental gains as shes constantly reminding me to not give her ALL the credit, as Im dedicated to my own fitness journey, putting in the work, and making changes. Clearly, I highly recommend trying some sessions with Ashley if she has availability!

Jogpaul is one of the hardest working trainers you re going to come across. He has poured years of blood sweat and tears into perfecting his craft and now he s sharing that experience with the rest of us. Working with Jogpaul is going to push you to places you weren t sure you could go and will help you develop the physique you ve been dreaming of. Trust his process, invest in yourself and enjoy reaping the rewards! You re in good hands with Jogpaul.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Garrett, Thank you for your 5 stars review. We love hearing our clients are thrilled to our personal training sessions. I know Jogpaul works super hard to make our club the bets place to achieve your fitness goals, so Ill sure to pass off your positive feedback to our team. Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: Hazel is always so happy and helpful.  She definitely makes my experience s lot easier when going to the gym.
reviews.response_from_owner_text: Hi Orla, Thank you for your review. I know Hazel works super hard to make our club the best place to achieve your fitness goals, so Ill be sure to pass off your positive feedback to them. Thanks again, Eve General Manager

reviews.review_text: Melissa, a personal trainer there, is honestly the best trainer Ive worked with! She motivates you and makes sure to push you to achieve your goals. She makes sure to teach you a lot about technique and is super friendly and fun to train with! Really recommend working with her!!

Ive been going here for 4+ years and I am really impressed with the effort that the new owners have put in. Theyve brought in several olympic platforms and a variety of benches and resistance machines to diversify the equipment. PT Adam is a fantastic trainer who is friendly, knowledgeable and inspiring. I would definitely recommend this gym.
Great gym! My personal trainer Chloe is very knowledgeable and professional. Im already seeing some improvements thanks to her help and dedication! Would highly recommend.

Needed to find a new gym to go and came across this gym. Very satisfied and had a great experience. One of the employees named Arvi who was very friendly showed me around to settle in and gave me some tips on how to use some machines. Looking forward to come back here again!
